message:
People from all walks of life joined the rallies in Assam today. Happy to see so many youngsters participate. Misgovernance in Assam has led to people facing immense difficulties. A stable Bharatiya Janata Party (BJP) Govt in Assam will completely transform the state. 

Assam polls are not about who the next MLA will be. They are about Assam's future. India will grow when Assam grows. http://nm-4.com/vmul
